<p>This picture sums up why I haven&rsquo;t been blogging for a while &ndash; I&rsquo;m now part of Google&rsquo;s search infrastructure engineering team, and I&rsquo;m a mother!</p>

<p>In other news, I&rsquo;ve updated my Meteor realtime maps example to work with 1.0.5. The changes were as simple as:</p>

<ol>
<li><code>meteor update</code></li>
<li>Replace the template helper methods with a call to <code>Template.helpers()</code> - here&rsquo;s an <a href="https://github.com/pkaushik/parties/commit/42295a2896237d953a5d5ff2a846ab474103aec2">example</a>.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/meteor/meteor/wiki/Using-Blaze#no-more-constant-isolate-or-preserve">Remove</a> the <code>#constant</code> guard around the map canvas div</li>
</ol>

